room_title: Escape room "Back in the 50s" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: Very fun! We played the 50's room and had a great time. Owners are really nice people. Would highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Back in the 50s" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: Visited Locked Room for my first experience doing an escape room activity. My group did the Diner room and it was awesome! Not too hard, but definitely not too easy! I highly recommend this place for a good time!

room_title: Escape room "Back in the 50s" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: Me and about 13 of coworkers went and played Back in the 50's & The Last Hour of the Titanic today. We had an absolute blast! I will be going back with friends and family in the future. The staff there are very kind and were great about coordinating everything in advance. Highly recommend Locked Room Omaha.
